### Wave Execution Matrix

| Wave | Quick | Standard | Deep | Exhaustive | Nuclear |
|------|-------|----------|------|------------|---------|
| 1 — Breadth | REQUIRED | REQUIRED | REQUIRED | REQUIRED | REQUIRED |
| 2 — Depth | — | REQUIRED | REQUIRED | REQUIRED | REQUIRED |
